                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. He was taken the same day, a tew hours afterwards, by the officers.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350615-name-1108" type="witnessName">
